      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet ja tas Kalps pats saz-\nes mihleju fatwu Kungu /\nt Seewu/ un fatwus Behr-\nes ne gribbu fwabbads iseet.\nTad buhs winna Kungam\nceekſch teem*Deerweem west/\ntad buhs winnam to pee\nn Durwitn/ jeb pee ta Sten-\nwest / un winna Kungam\ntam winna Aufi ar Jhlenu\not / un tam buhs winnam\nscham falpoht.\n"
    },
    {
