    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ja winna fawam Kungam\natihe / ka wiꞥsch to ne irr\nibá tsdewis/ tad buhs win-\nto likt ispirkt / winch ne\nto fweeschai Tautai pahr-\nwiltigi ar to darridamees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet ja wiꞥsch to fawam\nlam Lantibá isdohd/ tad win-\nar to buhs pehz tahs Mei-\nteefas darriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ja wiꞥsch tam weenu zit-\ntu nemm/ tad tam ne buhs win-\nnai no winnas Barribas / no\nwinnas Apfegga/un Peedshwo-\nschanas neneeka atraut.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ja wiꞥsch schahs trihs\nLeetas ne darrihs/ tad buhs win-\nna welti iseet bes Naudas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas weenu Zilweku fitt/\nka tas mirſt/ tam buhs nokan-\ntam tapt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet kas ar Wiltu ne irr\nus to gluḣnejs/ bet Deews irr to\nwinna Rohká lizzis ktuht / tad\nnofazzischu es tew kahou Weetu/\nkurp tam buhs behgt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ja kas prett fawu\nTuwaku blehdtag irr darrijees/\nwinnu wiltigi nokaudams / tad\nbuhs tew to ir no manna Altara\nnemt/ ka tas teek nokants.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ja kas fawu Tehwu/jeb\nfawu Mahti fitt / tam buhs no-\nfautam tapt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ja kas Zilweku fohg / un\nwinnu pahrdohd/ un tastohp pee\nwinna atrasts / tam buhs no-\nfautam tapt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas arridsan fawu Teh-\nwu/jeb fawu Mahti nolahd/tam\nbuhs nokautam tapt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ja Wihrs barrahs / un\nweens to ohtru fitt ar Akinini/\njeb ar Duhri/ ka tas ne mirſt /\nbet tam us Gultu ja-gull.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ja tas atkaž uszelfahs/\nun eet ahra ar fawu Speeki/ tad\nbuhs tam/ kas winnu fitte / ne-\nnoscedsigam buht/ winnam buhs\ntikfai maffaht / ko tas irr aiska-\n"
    }
